{
  "text": "For critical and super-critical nonlinearity p \u2265 5, the solitons are unstable by the gKdV flow. The instability phenomenon is quite different in the critical case (linear stability holds and the nonlinear instability is related to the scaling parameter) and in the super-critical case (linear exponential instability). Similar results exist for NLS. See [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] .",
  "correct_citation": {
